msgid ""
"This course is comprised of video and written instruction and paired with "
"quizzes and practical exercises."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:24
msgid ""
"This course is designed for anyone who is interested in using data from or "
"publishing data to GBIF. It is particularly useful for those who have a "
"desire to know more about GBIF and its place in the biodiversity community "
"and want to engage further with GBIF."
msgstr ""

